last_episode_to_air.name: Home is Where the Hauntleys Are
last_episode_to_air.overview: When the Scare B&B is selected to receive a prestigious award by Edna and the Historical Society, the Hauntleys hurriedly prepare the house.

name: Vampirina
overview: A young vampire girl faces the joys and trials of being the new kid in town when her family moves from Transylvania to Pennsylvania.

episodes.name: Going Batty
episodes.overview: Vampirina, also known as Vee, is very anxious about being able to make new friends after she and her family relocate from Transylvania to a new home in Pennsylvania, as she adjust to being the new kid in town, and adapting to the human world.

episodes.name: Scare B&B
episodes.overview: The B&B is open, but double booked with humans and vampires, causing problems.

episodes.name: The Sleepover
